⚙️ ENGINE LAYER (V1 DESIGN)
Python system responsibilities:
Parse JSON rhythm definitions
Convert cycle systems into step grids
Map logs into MIDI note events
Apply swing & velocity rules
Export .mid files
⚠️ V1 intentionally avoids exposing:
